🔐 Bit 2: User & Authorization Security
🔹 Core Idea:
Control who can do what in SAP
🔹 Best Practices:
Follow Least Privilege Principle
Avoid giving:
SAP_ALL
SAP_NEW
Use role-based access control (RBAC)
🔹 Important Topics:
Role design (Single & Composite roles)
Segregation of Duties (SoD)
Firefighter ID (Emergency access)
🔹 Security Risks:
Unauthorized access
Privilege escalation
Misconfigured roles
